    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Europos Parlamento biuras"@lt, "Ufficio di presidenza del Parlamento europeo"@it, "Euroopan parlamentin puhemiehistö"@fi, "Predsedníctvo Európskeho parlamentu"@sk, "Mesa del Parlamento Europeo"@es, "Euroopa Parlamendi juhatus"@et, "Бюро на Европейския парламент"@bg, "Mesa do Parlamento Europeu"@pt, "Prezydium Parlamentu Europejskiego"@pl, "Biroul Parlamentului European"@ro, "Predsjedništvo Europskog parlamenta"@hr, "Az Európai Parlament Elnöksége"@hu, "Europaparlamentets presidium"@sv, "Il-Bureau tal-Parlament Ewropew"@mt, "Προεδρείο του Ευρωπαϊκού Κοινοβουλίου"@el, "Biúró Pharlaimint na hEorpa"@ga, "Predsedstvo Evropskega parlamenta"@sl, "Bureau of the European Parliament"@en, "Předsednictvo Evropského parlamentu"@cs, "Bureau van het Europees Parlement"@nl, "Eiropas Parlamenta Prezidijs"@lv, "Bureau du Parlement européen"@fr, "Präsidium des Europäischen Parlaments"@de, "Europa-Parlamentets præsidium"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Bureau is the body that lays down rules for the European Parliament. It draws up Parliament’s preliminary draft budget and decides all administrative, staff and organisational matters. The Bureau consists of the President of the European Parliament, the 14 Vice-Presidents and the five Quaestors elected by Parliament for a period of two and a half years (which can be renewed)."@en;
